{
  "stem": "18572.2",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 26.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we-- I realize now, in retrospect, that we were both sort of outsiders for whatever reason.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And this young boy became Joel Schumacher, who's the famous director.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I recently wrote to him.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I-- going through all of this memory stuff, I said, I have to write to him and say listen--",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--I've been following your career--",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--and I think it's great.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But the two of us were the sort of-- the outside kids, you know?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was a very good student.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, I was, like, in all the honor classes, and I was in honor English and honor history.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was on the student court.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Yeah, I did all of the academic stuff.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, that was interesting, because I was so involved on the student court.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We once went to visit a-- an actual court.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And there were, like, five of us.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the judge went around and said to everybody, well, what do you want to be?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And this person said so on and so.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I must have been the only girl, because he came to me and he said, what would you like to be?",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I said I'd like to be an attorney.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And he sort of, like, said, oh, forget it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You know, not in those words, but more or less.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But I really-- I did not have that same-- this is-- we're talking now the '50s.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I did not think in terms of getting married.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I wanted to do something else.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't think so, you know?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I think, first of all, at this point, Israel had become independent, like the big push was over.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And once I was here, I really wanted to be very American.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was sort of tired of, like, going from language to language to language.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
